This configuration sets up an Elastic Beanstalk WebServer environment by first creating an IAM role (`eb_ec2_role`) and an associated instance profile (`eb_ec2_profile`). Additionally, it defines an Elastic Beanstalk application (`my_application`) and then creates an Elastic Beanstalk environment (`WebServerEnvironment`) using the defined solution and application.

