Note: Replace `"YOUR_ZONE_ID"` with the actual ID of the Route 53 hosted zone. The health checks and failover routing policy rely on specific host records, which you should adjust according to your actual FQDN and health check paths. The setup assumes that you have already configured the AWS Route 53 hosted zone for the domain you are configuring failover policies for.

