}
```

This configuration creates a Lambda function URL resource which references the existing Lambda function `example_lambda`. The URL resource requires specific attributes such as `auth_type`, `cors` configuration, and other related settings to ensure some specific properties. Adjust the configurations based on your specific requirements and permissions.

