Note: In Terraform there currently isn't direct support for AWS CloudWatch composite alarms as there is for other types of alarms. The above snippet indicates a composite alarm using custom metrics as an example. For actual AWS CloudWatch composite alarms, you would typically configure these using the AWS console or CLI directly.

